snippet.title: If 2020 Was A Person | Ashish Chanchlani | Kunal Chhabhria | Akash Dodeja | Simran Dhanwani
snippet.description:
You can download upGrad from the link below:
http://bit.ly/DownloadUpGrad

Iss baar bhi sab sach likhunga, Ye video ka idea @ashish chanchlani vines  ne diya... usse ek concept sochne bola aur usne 5..6 bheje.. but 2020 wala baad mein bana nahi sakte kyunki comments aaenge... abhi kyu daal rahe ho...2021 chal raha hai... iss liye humne ye bana diya... jis joke pe hassi aaegi woh Ashish ne likha hai aur jispe nahi aaegi woh maine...aur baaki ka @Jashan Sirwani  ne..


Cast: ACV Rozgaar Yojna ke harr sadasya ko kaam mila ismein
@Akash Dodeja @Simran Dhanwani @Rohit Sadhwani @Jashan Sirwani @Tanish Sirwani aur sabka seth @Anmol Sachar apne Andheri ke PentHouse mein chill kar rahe the...

Shoot toh humne color camera se kiya... Christopher Kedare ka dost.. Sid Kedare ne shoot kiya. 

Editing: Titanic Movie ke poster ke printout 5 rupaye mein bechne wala Tanish Sirwani ne edit kiya star ka... Uske baad thoda maine kiya aur Ashish ne music and sound effects lagaye 15 min mein..

Thumbnail: Jaane do...main nahi bataunga ki Grishim Nawani ne cutout kiya aur hum baaki mazdooro ne milke baaki ka thumbnail design kiya.

Upload karne mein late ho raha hai... 2 baje bola tha, 2:13 ho rahe hai.. iss liye description yaha khatam karte hai, baaki video dekh ke dosto ko zarur bhejna...

Fcuk U 2020

Happy New Year

#AshishChanchlani #KunalChhabhria #Acvians #FU2020

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada

Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi

snippet.title: New year 2021 muggulu by easy rangoli Suneetha || Amazing New year Kolam rangoli designs
snippet.description:
New year 2021 muggulu by easy rangoli Suneetha || Amazing New year Kolam rangoli designs.It is our tradition to draw kolam every day morning at the doorsteps.
There are many benefits of drawing kolam in front of the house.
It is auspicious and believes Goddess Lakshmi enters the house if kolam is drawn.
Kolam brings a lot of positive vibrations and energy to you and your home.
Draw kolam soon after you wake up and then do your prayers.
Kolam or rangoli ( ‡§∞‡§Ç‡§ó‡•ã‡§≤‡•Ä  ) is a part of Indian culture and transferred from generation to the next generation.
This ancient art form is also called as muggulu in parts of South India like Andhra Pradesh and Telangana.
People draw different creative rangoli kolam designs using kolam powder or muggu pindi which is 
actually crushed Lime stone powder available in different parts of India.
There are different types of rangoli or kolam designs like dots kolam, sikku kolam, padi kolam, Margazhi kolam.
People draw special rangoli designs for Festivals like Sankranthi (Pongal), Diwali (Deepavali), Vijaya Dashami (Dasara).
Women create deepam rangoli or kolam designs during Diwali festival time, create very big and Dhanurmasam muggulu (Margazhi) for Sankranthi or Pongal festival.
It is a belief among the people that drawing muggulu in front of the house in the early morning soon after wake brings
good fortune to them and their family.
People mix rice flour to limestone powder and prepare their own kolam powder. Muggulu can also be drawn with rice flour only.
These Beautiful and creative designs are decorated with flowers based on the occasion or festival.
#Newyear2021 #Newyear #Newyearkolam #Newyearmuggulu #Newyearrangoli

snippet.title: Remembering the Legend | Tribute to Kalabhavan Mani | Linto Kurian
snippet.description:
"REMEMBERING THE LEGEND"
A tribute to the legendary kalabhavan mani  ‚ù§Ô∏è

Kunnisseri Veettil Raman Mani (1 January 1971 ‚Äì 6 March 2016), better known by his stage name Kalabhavan Mani, was an Indian film actor and singer. Mani started his career as a mimicry artist with the Kalabhavan troupe. He had starred in over 200 films, including Malayalam, Tamil, Kannada and Telugu films, and was renowned for his humorous characters and villain roles.

Mani won the National Film Award ‚Äì Special Jury Award and Kerala State Film Award for his performance as Ramu in Vasanthiyum Lakshmiyum Pinne Njaanum (1999).

snippet.title: Phish "Dinner And A Rematch" Madison Square Garden ‚Äî 12/31/95
snippet.description:
Exactly 25 years after the audience tied the band 1-1 in a chess rivalry, Phish challenges YOU to a rematch as part of a special New Year‚Äôs Eve ‚ÄúDinner And A Movie‚Äù. We‚Äôll be presenting Phish‚Äôs first New Year‚Äôs Eve show from Madison Square Garden ‚Äî 12/31/95 ‚Äî in its entirety, beginning at 8:30 pm ET.

We‚Äôve teamed up with the fine folks at https://Chess.com to host the Band vs. Audience online chess game which will start right at the top of the show and move at a decent clip. In short, fans will have 5 minutes to move their piece (the band will have no more than that as well). At the end of 5 minutes, whichever move has the most votes is the ‚Äòaudience‚Äô move. Stick around during the set breaks as the band joins in from their various homes, playing a few moves and providing scintillating commentary on the game. We will post and send out the actual game link on 12/31.

To pace yourself over a long evening, we present some chess cheese board recipes for extended grazing. Our friend Marissa Mullen put together two options ‚Äî ‚ÄúOlive Cheese Dreams‚Äù and ‚ÄúBilly Bries‚Äù ‚Äî with an easy ‚Äòcheese by numbers‚Äô guide. Feel free to swap out any of the ingredients if there‚Äôs something else you prefer. Pair with the bubbly of your choice. For dessert, chessboard cookies! Recipes can be found at https://livephi.sh/chessmenu

For this final webcast of the year, our beneficiary will be none other than The WaterWheel Foundation itself. Since 1997, the band and their fans have collaborated on a nationwide charitable endeavor by raising funds and donating the proceeds across the country. This year alone, collectively we have raised and donated nearly $750,000 to 27 different nonprofits during the Dinner And A Movie series. Join us in continuing to support those in need. Donate at https://www.phish.com/waterwheel

snippet.title: Welcome to BREATH - A 30 Day Yoga Journey  |  Yoga With Adriene
snippet.description:
It is happening! Today‚Äôs video is a bit of an orientation, a warm welcome, and an official kick-off. We will begin with a few easy group breaths to enjoy, and recognize that if all you do is arrive here to breathe, you are winning, golden, exactly where you are meant to be. 

You can consider this a practice day for your upcoming practices if you like. 

**IMPORTANT** If you are not signed up for the daily email that corresponds with each practice video, sign up for free and receive your free BREATH calendar here: https://www.yogawithadriene.com/breath

Work with what you have, but in this video, I make some suggestions on some optional things you might like to bring to class each day, along with an invitation to help guide you as you embark on this unique journey. 

Check-in with your willingness to be present, and remember for this to take off - you have to show up.

If this cross-legged position is not doable for you, you can use blankets, blocks, or pillows to sit up on. You can also come into a chair, or on the edge of your couch when we take this shape. That is a great way to modify and possibly a better spot for you to tune in, work with the breath technique, and warm up before we get moving into other shapes each day. 

Finally, set an intention. Be brave and ask WHY? Why are you here? What do you think pulled you here? And if you don‚Äôt know, that is okay, we will likely uncover that together. (How exciting!)

Let me know where you are practicing from in the comment section down below!

snippet.title: LAKERS at SPURS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | December 30, 2020
snippet.description:
LAKERS at SPURS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | December 30, 2020

LeBron James (26 PTS, 5 REB, 8 AST) led the Los Angeles Lakers to a 121-107 win over the San Antonio Spurs. With his 26 PTS, James has now scored 10+ PTS in 1,000-consecutive outings. Anthony Davis finished with 20 PTS and 8 REB, and Dennis Schroder supplied 21 PTS in the win. Dejounte Murray led the way for the Spurs with a career-high 29 PTS, 7 REB and 7 AST, and DeMar DeRozan provided 23 PTS and 6 AST for San Antonio.

snippet.title: HORNETS at MAVERICKS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | December 30, 2020
snippet.description:
HORNETS at MAVERICKS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | December 30, 2020

The Charlotte Hornets defeated the Dallas Mavericks 118-99. The Charlotte bench led the way in the win as rookie LaMelo Ball finished with a team-high 22 PTS, 9 REB and 5 AST, and Miles Bridges added 20 PTS and 16 REB. Tim Hardaway Jr. led the scoring attack for the Mavericks with 18 PTS, and Luka Doncic finished with 12 PTS and 5 AST.

snippet.title: Welcome to BREATH - A 30 Day Yoga Journey  |  Yoga With Adriene
snippet.description:
It is happening! Today‚Äôs video is a bit of an orientation, a warm welcome, and an official kick-off. We will begin with a few easy group breaths to enjoy, and recognize that if all you do is arrive here to breathe, you are winning, golden, exactly where you are meant to be. 

You can consider this a practice day for your upcoming practices if you like. 

**IMPORTANT** If you are not signed up for the daily email that corresponds with each practice video, sign up for free and receive your free BREATH calendar here: https://www.yogawithadriene.com/breath

Work with what you have, but in this video, I make some suggestions on some optional things you might like to bring to class each day, along with an invitation to help guide you as you embark on this unique journey. 

Check-in with your willingness to be present, and remember for this to take off - you have to show up.

If this cross-legged position is not doable for you, you can use blankets, blocks, or pillows to sit up on. You can also come into a chair, or on the edge of your couch when we take this shape. That is a great way to modify and possibly a better spot for you to tune in, work with the breath technique, and warm up before we get moving into other shapes each day. 

Finally, set an intention. Be brave and ask WHY? Why are you here? What do you think pulled you here? And if you don‚Äôt know, that is okay, we will likely uncover that together. (How exciting!)

Let me know where you are practicing from in the comment section down below!

snippet.title: New Year's 2021: Dubai puts on dazzling fireworks show from iconic Burj Khalifa
snippet.description:
The United Arab Emirates welcomed the new year in Dubai with a mesmerizing display of lights, fireworks and music from the world's tallest building, the iconic Burj Khalifa. 

The light show paid tribute to front-line health workers amid the coronavirus pandemic and displayed words of hope for 2021.

The UAE has imposed restrictions to slow the spread of COVID-19 on New Year‚Äôs Eve, including limiting social gatherings to 30 and under, and masks must be worn.

For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/7548867/new-years-eve-2020-coronavirus/

snippet.title: WELCOME TO THE OTHER SIDE (NYE in virtual Notre Dame)
snippet.description:
Join & share the party on December 31st, 2020 at 23:25 (CET) & Paris-time!
Go to www.jeanmicheljarre.com to see how you can watch on Facebook, Twitter, VR, TV and Radio. 
WELCOME TO THE OTHER SIDE (The Album) is out now https://JMJ.lnk.to/WTTOSAW


**ENGLISH BELOW**

En partenariat avec la @Ville de Paris et sous le patronage de l'@UNESCO, le pionnier de la musique √©lectronique @jeanmicheljarre s'associe √† la start-up fran√ßaise VRrOOm pour nous emmener vers la nouvelle ann√©e avec un concert-spectacle innovant en  live-stream se d√©roulant depuis la c√©l√®bre cath√©drale, Notre-Dame de Paris, en virtuelle et mod√©lis√©e pour l‚Äôoccasion. 

 ¬´Welcome to the Other Side¬ª est une exp√©rience de concert gratuite unique, mondiale et ouverte √† tous, dont l'ambition, au-del√† de c√©l√©brer la nouvelle ann√©e de mani√®re futuriste et festive, est d'envoyer un message d'espoir pour 2021 et pour la fin des temps sombres que nous traversons tous cette ann√©e: une invitation num√©rique et virtuelle de Paris, Ville Lumi√®re, m√©tropole anim√©e des Arts et de la Culture,  abritant la cath√©drale la plus c√©l√®bre au monde. Notre-Dame a une place unique dans l'imaginaire collectif, c'est un symbole de la force et du patrimoine mondial qui nous unit. 

Pour plus d‚Äôinformations, rejoignez et suivez JMJ sur Facebook, Twitter, Instagram & YouTube, ou consultez :
www.jeanmicheljarre.com

Suivez Jean-Michel Jarre sur :
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jeanmicheljarre/



Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/jeanmicheljarre
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jeanmicheljarre/
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/user/jeanmicheljarre?sub_confirmation=1

___________________________________________ 


In partnership with @Ville de Paris, and under the patronage of @UNESCO, Electronic Music pioneer @jeanmicheljarre teams up with French VR start-up VRrOOm to take us into the New Year with a Live-stream trailblazing concert-spectacular set in the virtual environment of the planetary landmark, Notre-Dame de Paris.

‚ÄúWelcome to the Other Side‚Äù is a one-off exclusive, worldwide and open-to-all, free concert experience whose ambition, beyond celebrating the New Year in a futuristic and festive way, is to send a message of hope for 2021 and for the end of the dark times we are all going through this year: a digital and virtual invitation from Paris, the City of Light, vibrant metropole of the Arts & of Culture and home to the most famous cathedral in the world. Notre-Dame has a unique place in the collective imagination, it is a symbol of the strength and of World Heritage that binds us together.  
 
For all ongoing information follow JMJ on Facebook, Twitter, Instagram and YouTube or check: www.jeanmicheljarre.com
 
Follow Jean-Michel Jarre:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jeanmicheljarre/ 
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/jeanmicheljarre 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jeanmicheljarre/
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/user/jeanmicheljarre?sub_confirmation=1

----
How to watch via Youtube, Facebook, Twitter, TV, radio or VR: for full details check www.jeanmicheljarre.com 

Here is how to join the VR experience: 

6DoF Concert:
- Download the VRChat app on Steam, Oculus or Viveport to watch the concert in virtual reality on all PC VR headsets, Oculus Quest and Quest 2 + link cable, or simply via PC
Once in VRChat, check the 'NOTRE-DAME CONCERT' icon in the WORLDS menu to access the concert. Attention, the world will be activated on December 31 at 11:23pm CET only (December 31 at 2:23pm PST).
Quest and Quest 2 users who are not equipped with the link cable will be able to access a lighter version of the concert!
REPLAYS WILL BE AVAILABLE TO ALL FOR 24 HOURS!

6DoF After-party:
- Download the VRChat app on Steam, Oculus or Viveport to watch the concert in virtual reality on all PC VR headsets, Oculus Quest and Quest 2 with or without link cable, or simply via PC
Once in VRChat, check the 'NOTRE-DAME AFTER-PARTY' icon in the WORLDS menu to access the party. Attention, the world will be activated starting January 1 at 00:13pm CET only (December 31 at 3:13pm PST).
Many suprises await you in the after-party world!
REPLAYS WILL BE AVAILABLE TO ALL FOR 4 DAYS UNTIL JANUARY 4!

3DoF Concert will be accessible inside Oculus Venues, from December 31 at 11:25pm to January 4.

#VR #NYE #NotreDame

snippet.title: New Year's 2021: Sydney, Australia puts on stunning fireworks display
snippet.description:
Sydney, Australia put on a stunning fireworks show from Sydney Harbour Bridge and over the iconic Sydney Opera House to ring in 2021. In past years, 1 million people crowded the harbour to watch fireworks, but most watched on television this year as authorities urge residents to stay home due to the coronavirus pandemic.

Australia was among the first nations to usher in the New Year because of its proximity to the International Date Line, but is a grim end to the year for New South Wales and Victoria, the country‚Äôs two most populous states, which are battling to curb new COVID-19 outbreaks.

For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/7548867/new-years-eve-2020-coronavirus/

snippet.title: !@#$%$#!! || Dubov vs Carlsen || Airthings Masters (2020)
snippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Daniil Dubov vs Magnus Carlsen
Airthings Masters (2020), Round Quarterfinals, Game 3
Queen's pawn game (E10)

1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 d5 4. g3 Bb4+ 5. Nbd2 dxc4 6. Bg2 a5 7. a3 Bxd2+ 8. Bxd2 b5 9. a4 c6 10. Qc2 Bb7 11. h4 Nbd7 12. h5 h6 13. Ne5 Nd5 14. Rh4 N7f6 15. Kf1 Qc7 16. Kg1 Nb4 17. Qc1 Rd8 18. axb5 cxb5 19. Bxb4 axb4 20. Ra7 Nd5 21. Rg4 Rg8 22. Qc2 c3 23. bxc3 bxc3 24. Ra3 Rc8 25. Nd3 Nf6 26. Bxb7 Qxb7 27. Nc5 Rxc5 28. dxc5 Nxg4 29. c6 Qxc6 30. Rxc3 Qb6 31. e3 Ke7 32. Rc6 Qd8 33. Qc5+ Kf6 34. Rd6 Qe7 35. Qd4+ Kg5 36. f3 f5 37. fxg4 Rc8 38. Qf4+ Kf6 39. Qxf5#

World Chess Champion Magnus Carlsen tops the field for the Airthings Masters, the 2nd stage of the Champions Chess Tour. The 12-player event will be played online on chess24 from December 26th to January 3rd and, as the first Major of the tour, features a $200,000 prize fund with $60,000 for 1st place. The winner also qualifies directly to the Grand Final in September 2021.

The tournament starts with a 3-day preliminary stage where the players play each other once before the top 8 go forward to a knockout. The time control is 15 minutes for all moves, with a 10-second increment from move 1. No draw offers are allowed before move 40. Official website: championschesstour.com

localizations.en-US.title: !@#$%$#!! || Dubov vs Carlsen || Airthings Masters (2020)
localizations.en-US.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Daniil Dubov vs Magnus Carlsen
Airthings Masters (2020), Round Quarterfinals, Game 3
Queen's pawn game (E10)

1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 d5 4. g3 Bb4+ 5. Nbd2 dxc4 6. Bg2 a5 7. a3 Bxd2+ 8. Bxd2 b5 9. a4 c6 10. Qc2 Bb7 11. h4 Nbd7 12. h5 h6 13. Ne5 Nd5 14. Rh4 N7f6 15. Kf1 Qc7 16. Kg1 Nb4 17. Qc1 Rd8 18. axb5 cxb5 19. Bxb4 axb4 20. Ra7 Nd5 21. Rg4 Rg8 22. Qc2 c3 23. bxc3 bxc3 24. Ra3 Rc8 25. Nd3 Nf6 26. Bxb7 Qxb7 27. Nc5 Rxc5 28. dxc5 Nxg4 29. c6 Qxc6 30. Rxc3 Qb6 31. e3 Ke7 32. Rc6 Qd8 33. Qc5+ Kf6 34. Rd6 Qe7 35. Qd4+ Kg5 36. f3 f5 37. fxg4 Rc8 38. Qf4+ Kf6 39. Qxf5#

World Chess Champion Magnus Carlsen tops the field for the Airthings Masters, the 2nd stage of the Champions Chess Tour. The 12-player event will be played online on chess24 from December 26th to January 3rd and, as the first Major of the tour, features a $200,000 prize fund with $60,000 for 1st place. The winner also qualifies directly to the Grand Final in September 2021.

The tournament starts with a 3-day preliminary stage where the players play each other once before the top 8 go forward to a knockout. The time control is 15 minutes for all moves, with a 10-second increment from move 1. No draw offers are allowed before move 40. Official website: championschesstour.com

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | ARSENAL 1-4 MAN CITY | CARABAO CUP
snippet.description:
Holders Manchester City produced another Carabao Cup masterclass as we secured a comprehensive last-eight victory over Arsenal in North London to march into the semi-finals.

Second-half strikes from Riyad Mahrez, Phil Foden and Aymeric Laporte made it a night to remember after Gabriel Jesus‚Äôs third-minute opener had been cancelled out before the break.

The victory further extended manager Pep Guardiola‚Äôs incredible record in the League Cup and was no less than we deserved after what was another impressive all-round display.

Match report: https://www.mancity.com/news/mens/arsenal-v-manchester-city-carabao-cup-report-63744261

snippet.title: A K -Drama Kiss - The BenZi Project
snippet.description:
#TheBENZIproject
Benjamin Kheng & Hirzi Zulkiflie
________________________________________________________________

A K-DRAMA KISS
Two long-lost lovers finally meet after years apart. Will they kiss, is there a twist, and how long is this theme song?

A K-Drama Kiss is supported by the National Arts Council as part of the #SGCultureAnywhere campaign. 

Co-produced by: Stardust Story

STARRING
Hirzi Zulkiflie
Benjamin Kheng

Directed & Written by Benjamin Kheng
Produced by: Hirzi Zulkiflie & Skye Chen
Line Producer: Catherine Therese Zhang Binbin
Director of Photography: Bong
1st Assistant Director:  Skye Chen
Production Manager: Sam Chua
Production Assistant: Fiona Ng & Qayyum Lukman
Safety Officer: Huimin
1st Camera Assistant: Matthew Chong
Sound Recordist: Wesley Meow
Grip: Melvin Han
Art  Director: Hirzi Zulkiflie
Art Assistant: Claudia Park & Shermaine Law
Hair / Make-up  Artist: Norehan Fong-Harun
Stylist: Violet Foo
Score: Benjamin Kheng 
Editor/Graphics: Qing

SPONSORS
True Colour Media
Wheeler's Estate

SPECIAL THANKS
Ekamatra
Holy Moly
The White Dojo
Xavier

--------------------------------------------------

COMEDY WITH BITE.

The BenZi Project is comedy sketch series aimed at making you laugh, then think, then cry uncontrollably in existential dread (in that order). The brainchild of Singaporean-based actors and writers Benjamin Kheng (of The Sam Willows) and Hirzi Zulkiflie (of MunahHirziOfficial), BenZi exists in the same world as mermaid frappuccinos and beer yoga, as the show no one asked for or deserves, but is going to get anyway. 

FACEBOOK, INSTAGRAM ‚Äî @thebenziproject
CONTACT US ‚Äî hello@thebenziproject.com

BENJAMIN KHENG 
Facebook - fb.com/benjamin.kheng
Instagram - @benjaminkheng
Twitter -  @benjaminkheng

HIRZI
Facebook - fb.com/hirziofficial 
Instagram - @hirziofficial
Twitter - @hirziofficial

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | CITY 2-0 NEWCASTLE | GUNDOGAN & TORRES
snippet.description:
City moved up to into the top five of the Premier League with an impressive 2-0 Boxing Day win over Newcastle United.

Gundogan and Torres on target as City see off Newcastle
Despite appalling conditions with rain and gale force winds lashing the Etihad, Pep Guardiola‚Äôs side went about their work in fine style.

Ilkay Gundogan struck early in the first half to give City a deserved lead ‚Äì and Ferran Torres then added to our advantage with a second goal soon after the restart.

snippet.title: Watch New Zealand's 2021 New Year fireworks display
snippet.description:
Kick-off New Year's Eve with Auckland, New Zealand, as the first major city to celebrate 2021.

It is expected we will see a vast laser display followed by an impressive show of fireworks. 

Auckland will be one of the few cities able to bid farewell to 2020 in style, as several cities including London and Las Vegas have cancelled their December 31 displays to prevent large crowds from gathering during the Covid-19 pandemic. 

Australia, who celebrate New Year's Eve just a few hours after New Zealand, will also allow events but under strict restrictions. 

Subscribe to The Telegraph on YouTube ‚ñ∫ https://bit.ly/3idrdLH

Get the latest headlines: https://www.telegraph.co.uk/

Telegraph.co.uk and YouTube.com/TelegraphTV are websites of The Telegraph, the UK's best-selling quality daily newspaper providing news and analysis on UK and world events, business, sport, lifestyle and culture.

snippet.title: Glitterbomb 3.0 vs. Porch Pirates
snippet.description:
Merry Christmas ya filthy animals.  If you want to learn the design fundamentals it takes to make something like the Glitter Bomb, enroll in my NEW Creative Engineering course at https://Monthly.com/MarkRober and I'll see you in class!

MY NEW MERCH!!!  https://markrober.store/

Thanks to SimpliSafe for providing the cameras.  Check out their biggest sale of the year by visiting http://simplisafe.com/markrober

Subscribe to Jim's channel here- https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBNG0osIBAprVcZZ3ic84vw

Biodegradable glitter courtesy of  https://www.altnaturals.com/pages/glitter

So stoked to finally announce my creative engineering class has just launched today! Enrollment is now open until Dec 27 at Monthly.com/MarkRober (link also in bio).

This class is a hands-on, 30-day learning experience that will teach you how to use engineering and science to bring your creative ideas to life.

During this class, I'm going to share with you my entire creative engineering process from start to finish. You're going to follow along with me as I fully design and engineer 3 brand new builds from scratch... from how I come up the idea, all the way through bringing the final builds to life.

The best part is, over the month, you'll follow along with me and my process, side by side, and you will leave the class with 3 original, creative builds of your own.

This is the class I wish I had when I was starting out. It's designed to take your skills to make cool stuff to the next level, whether you're a beginner or a more experienced maker/engineer.

The class officially starts on January 4, 2021, and it will only run a few times per year, so claim your spot if you're interested!

See you in class!

-Mark

snippet.title: Watch Australia's 2021 Sydney Harbour New Year fireworks celebrations
snippet.description:
Watch a 'toned down' firework display in Sydney Harbour this year, as Australia allows New Year's Eve events to happen, but under strict rules and restrictions. 

Anyone who wished to enter the Sydney Harbour 'Green Zone' on New Year's Eve needed to apply for an entry pass, with prime firework vantage points being designated for frontline workers.

People have been encouraged to limit non-essential gatherings over the New Year period where possible to further minimise the risk of transmission in the community.

MAHALAGANG PAALALA:

Muli po naming pinapaalala na hanggang ngayon ay SARADO PA RIN PO ANG AMING ACTION CENTER sa TV5 Media Center, Reliance Street, Mandaluyong City.

Hindi pa rin po maaaring pumunta nang personal ang mga complainant para magreklamo kay Idol Raffy dahil sa ating kinahaharap na pandemya at mahigpit pa ring ipinapatupad ang mga safety measures upang maging ligtas ang lahat.

Maraming salamat sa inyong pag-unawa at mag-ingat po tayong lahat!

snippet.title: The Beatles:  Get Back - A Sneak Peek from Peter Jackson
snippet.description:
PETER JACKSON REVEALS SNEAK PEEK OF HIS UPCOMING MUSIC DOCUMENTARY
‚ÄúTHE BEATLES: GET BACK‚Äù ONLINE AND STREAMING ON DISNEY+ 

Feature-Length Film Opens in Theatres August 27, 2021

Acclaimed filmmaker Peter Jackson has released an exclusive sneak peek of his upcoming documentary ‚ÄúThe Beatles: Get Back‚Äù for fans everywhere to enjoy. The 5-minute special look is available to fans worldwide on TheBeatles.com and streaming on Disney+.
 
Jackson said, ‚ÄúWe wanted to give the fans of The Beatles all over the world a holiday treat, so we put together this five-minute sneak peek at our upcoming theatrical film ‚ÄòThe Beatles: Get Back.‚Äô We hope it will bring a smile to everyone‚Äôs faces and some much-needed joy at this difficult time.‚Äù

Acclaimed filmmaker Peter Jackson‚Äôs ‚ÄúThe Beatles: Get Back‚Äù is a unique cinematic experience that takes audiences back in time to The Beatles‚Äô intimate recording sessions during a pivotal moment in music history... 

Read more at https://www.thebeatles.com/news/beatles-get-back-sneak-peek-peter-jackson

#TheBeatlesGetBack

snippet.title: Neujahrsansprache 2021 von Bundeskanzlerin Angela Merkel
snippet.description:
In ihrer Neujahrsansprache dankt Kanzlerin Merkel den Deutschen f√ºr ihre Geduld, sich auf diesen historischen Kraftakt der Virus-Bek√§mpfung einzulassen. Die schwere Zeit f√ºr unser Land sei noch nicht vorbei. Mit den ersten Geimpften habe aber jetzt die Hoffnung Gesichter. 

Viele seien √ºber sich hinausgewachsen, ohne dies an die gro√üe Glocke zu h√§ngen, so Merkel - etwa  √Ñrzt*innen und Pflegekr√§fte, Mitarbeiter der Gesundheits√§mter und die Bundeswehr. Unz√§hlige h√§tten zudem dazu beigetragen, dass das Leben trotz Pandemie weiter m√∂glich sei.

Merkel wandte sich scharf gegen Versuche, die Gesundheitsgefahr generell in Zweifel zu ziehen. Die Kanzlerin betonte, am Ende eines "atemlosen Jahres" gelte es auch, innezuhalten und zu trauern. Viele h√§tten einen geliebten Menschen verloren. Sie k√∂nne nur ahnen, wie bitter es sich f√ºr diese Menschen anf√ºhlen m√ºsse, wenn von einigen Unverbesserlichen das Virus bestritten und geleugnet werde.

----- 

Hier auf ZDFheute Nachrichten erfahrt ihr, was auf der Welt passiert und was uns alle etwas angeht: Wir sorgen f√ºr Durchblick in der Nachrichtenwelt, erkl√§ren die Hintergr√ºnde und gehen auf gesellschaftliche Debatten ein. Diskutiert in Livestreams mit uns und bildet euch eure eigene Meinung mit den Fakten, die wir euch pr√§sentieren.

Abonniert unseren Kanal, um nichts mehr zu verpassen.

Immer auf dem aktuellen Stand seid ihr auf http://www.ZDFheute.de/.

snippet.title: WELCOME TO THE OTHER SIDE (NYE in virtual Notre Dame)
snippet.description:
Join & share the party on December 31st, 2020 at 23:25 (CET) & Paris-time!
Go to www.jeanmicheljarre.com to see how you can watch on Facebook, Twitter, VR, TV and Radio. 
WELCOME TO THE OTHER SIDE (The Album) is out now https://JMJ.lnk.to/WTTOSAW


**ENGLISH BELOW**

En partenariat avec la @Ville de Paris et sous le patronage de l'@UNESCO, le pionnier de la musique √©lectronique @jeanmicheljarre s'associe √† la start-up fran√ßaise VRrOOm pour nous emmener vers la nouvelle ann√©e avec un concert-spectacle innovant en  live-stream se d√©roulant depuis la c√©l√®bre cath√©drale, Notre-Dame de Paris, en virtuelle et mod√©lis√©e pour l‚Äôoccasion. 

 ¬´Welcome to the Other Side¬ª est une exp√©rience de concert gratuite unique, mondiale et ouverte √† tous, dont l'ambition, au-del√† de c√©l√©brer la nouvelle ann√©e de mani√®re futuriste et festive, est d'envoyer un message d'espoir pour 2021 et pour la fin des temps sombres que nous traversons tous cette ann√©e: une invitation num√©rique et virtuelle de Paris, Ville Lumi√®re, m√©tropole anim√©e des Arts et de la Culture,  abritant la cath√©drale la plus c√©l√®bre au monde. Notre-Dame a une place unique dans l'imaginaire collectif, c'est un symbole de la force et du patrimoine mondial qui nous unit. 

Pour plus d‚Äôinformations, rejoignez et suivez JMJ sur Facebook, Twitter, Instagram & YouTube, ou consultez :
www.jeanmicheljarre.com

Suivez Jean-Michel Jarre sur :
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jeanmicheljarre/



Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/jeanmicheljarre
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jeanmicheljarre/
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/user/jeanmicheljarre?sub_confirmation=1

___________________________________________ 


In partnership with @Ville de Paris, and under the patronage of @UNESCO, Electronic Music pioneer @jeanmicheljarre teams up with French VR start-up VRrOOm to take us into the New Year with a Live-stream trailblazing concert-spectacular set in the virtual environment of the planetary landmark, Notre-Dame de Paris.

‚ÄúWelcome to the Other Side‚Äù is a one-off exclusive, worldwide and open-to-all, free concert experience whose ambition, beyond celebrating the New Year in a futuristic and festive way, is to send a message of hope for 2021 and for the end of the dark times we are all going through this year: a digital and virtual invitation from Paris, the City of Light, vibrant metropole of the Arts & of Culture and home to the most famous cathedral in the world. Notre-Dame has a unique place in the collective imagination, it is a symbol of the strength and of World Heritage that binds us together.  
 
For all ongoing information follow JMJ on Facebook, Twitter, Instagram and YouTube or check: www.jeanmicheljarre.com
 
Follow Jean-Michel Jarre:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jeanmicheljarre/ 
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/jeanmicheljarre 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jeanmicheljarre/
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/user/jeanmicheljarre?sub_confirmation=1

----
How to watch via Youtube, Facebook, Twitter, TV, radio or VR: for full details check www.jeanmicheljarre.com 

Here is how to join the VR experience: 

6DoF Concert:
- Download the VRChat app on Steam, Oculus or Viveport to watch the concert in virtual reality on all PC VR headsets, Oculus Quest and Quest 2 + link cable, or simply via PC
Once in VRChat, check the 'NOTRE-DAME CONCERT' icon in the WORLDS menu to access the concert. Attention, the world will be activated on December 31 at 11:23pm CET only (December 31 at 2:23pm PST).
Quest and Quest 2 users who are not equipped with the link cable will be able to access a lighter version of the concert!
REPLAYS WILL BE AVAILABLE TO ALL FOR 24 HOURS!

6DoF After-party:
- Download the VRChat app on Steam, Oculus or Viveport to watch the concert in virtual reality on all PC VR headsets, Oculus Quest and Quest 2 with or without link cable, or simply via PC
Once in VRChat, check the 'NOTRE-DAME AFTER-PARTY' icon in the WORLDS menu to access the party. Attention, the world will be activated starting January 1 at 00:13pm CET only (December 31 at 3:13pm PST).
Many suprises await you in the after-party world!
REPLAYS WILL BE AVAILABLE TO ALL FOR 4 DAYS UNTIL JANUARY 4!

3DoF Concert will be accessible inside Oculus Venues, from December 31 at 11:25pm to January 4.

#VR #NYE #NotreDame

snippet.title: Zerst√∂re 2020 - Die Challenge II Das schaffst du nie!
snippet.description:
Ciao 2020, es war  sch√∂nwar sch√∂n mit dir - NICHT! Deshalb lassen wir es bei ‚ÄûDas schaffst du nie!‚Äú zum Jahresende so richtig knallen und zerst√∂ren das Jahr 2020! Genauer gesagt: Sebastian Meinberg aka der Zerst√∂rer √ºbernimmt das h√∂chstpers√∂nlich. In dieser DSDN-Challenge soll Meini, stellvertretend f√ºr die ganze Welt und im pers√∂nlichen Auftrag von Marc Seibold, das Jahr 2020 so richtig kaputt machen. 2020 soll brennen, auseinander fallenauseinanderfallen, durchbrochen und zerschossen werden! FCK 2020!
 
MEINI VS. 2020 

Auf Sebastian Meinberg lastet wohl der bisher gr√∂√üte Druck seines Lebens: Bei der ‚ÄûDas schaffst du nie!‚Äú-Silvester-Challenge muss er 2020 zerst√∂ren. Wenn Meini das nicht schafft, wird 2021 genauso weitergehen. Das w√§re wohl wirklich das Worst Case Szenario! Und eine Strafe f√ºr uns alle! Deshalb: Go Meini, Go Meini! Doch wie zu erwarten, bringt die DSDN-Zerst√∂r-Challenge von Marc Seibold nat√ºrlich auch Schwierigkeiten mit sich. Schlie√ülich hat sich das Jahr 2020 schon so in unsere K√∂pfe, Herzen und Leben eingebrannt, dass sich das nicht mal eben so kaputt machen l√§sst!  Meini wird aber alles geben, um dem Jahr 2020 an seinem letzten Tag zu zeigen, was es uns alles angetan hat! 

SO WAR DAS DSDN-JAHR 2020 

Mit einer fulminanten Zerst√∂r-Challenge verabschieden wir uns vom Jahr 2020! Was haben wir dieses Jahr nicht alles erlebt bei ‚ÄûDas schaffst du nie!‚Äú. Wir starteten mit der 24 Stunden Insel-Challenge und der darauffolgenden, hei√ü ersehnten Achterbahnstrafe f√ºr Marc ins Jahr. Wir f√ºhrten unsere neue Reihe ‚ÄûDSDN Classics‚Äú ein, Ari telefonierte ganz 24 Stunden mit euch, Marc musste endlich alle seine Sozialstrafen ableisten, wir machten drei knallharte Verstecken-Challenges, Meini musste 24 Stunden Autoscooter fahren und und und. Es ging hoch hinaus und wieder tief hinunter, es war eiskalt und wurde richtig hei√ü, es war schmerzhaft, peinlich und unfassbar lustig. Und das alles war wieder mal nur m√∂glich dank eurer gro√üartigen Unterst√ºtzung! Danke liebe DSDN-Community f√ºr euren Support, eure Kommentare und Likes, euer Lob und eure Kritik und die viele Liebe. Wir sehen uns 2021 - wenn hoffentlich alles besser wird. (habe beim Lesen eine kleine Tr√§ne wegdr√ºcken m√ºssen) 

Welches DSDN Video hat euch im Jahr 2020 am‚ÄØbesten‚ÄØund welches am wenigsten gefallen? Schreibt es uns in die Kommentare!‚ÄØ 

 

#DSDN #Dasschaffstdunie #funk #Challenge 

******************************************************************** 

Ob 72 Stunden moderieren, eine Skischanze hochrennen oder eine Skulptur aus Eis schnitzen: Bei ‚ÄûDas schaffst du nie!‚Äú stellt der fiese Redakteur Marc Seibold den zwei Hosts Ariane Alter und Sebastian Meinberg immer abwechselnd eine Challenge ‚Äì gerne auch 24 Stunden lang. Schaffen die Hosts die Challenge, d√ºrfen sie Marc bestrafen. Schaffen sie es nicht, m√ºssen sie noch eine Bestrafung ertragen. Jeden Donnerstag um 15 Uhr gibt‚Äôs ein neues Video von ‚ÄûDas schaffst du nie!‚Äú. Heute: Die Zerst√∂r-Challenge! Auf jede neue Challenge kommt am darauffolgenden Donnerstag die Bestrafung.  

Wer Sebastian bei der n√§chsten Challenge sehen m√∂chte, klickt hier: https://www.instagram.com/heinz.wescher/ 

Und wer Marc folgen m√∂chte, klickt hier: https://instagram.com/marc_cyborg ‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨‚ñ¨

snippet.localized.title: Zerst√∂re 2020 - Die Challenge II Das schaffst du nie!
snippet.localized.description:
Ciao 2020, es war  sch√∂nwar sch√∂n mit dir - NICHT! Deshalb lassen wir es bei ‚ÄûDas schaffst du nie!‚Äú zum Jahresende so richtig knallen und zerst√∂ren das Jahr 2020! Genauer gesagt: Sebastian Meinberg aka der Zerst√∂rer √ºbernimmt das h√∂chstpers√∂nlich. In dieser DSDN-Challenge soll Meini, stellvertretend f√ºr die ganze Welt und im pers√∂nlichen Auftrag von Marc Seibold, das Jahr 2020 so richtig kaputt machen. 2020 soll brennen, auseinander fallenauseinanderfallen, durchbrochen und zerschossen werden! FCK 2020!
 
MEINI VS. 2020 

Auf Sebastian Meinberg lastet wohl der bisher gr√∂√üte Druck seines Lebens: Bei der ‚ÄûDas schaffst du nie!‚Äú-Silvester-Challenge muss er 2020 zerst√∂ren. Wenn Meini das nicht schafft, wird 2021 genauso weitergehen. Das w√§re wohl wirklich das Worst Case Szenario! Und eine Strafe f√ºr uns alle! Deshalb: Go Meini, Go Meini! Doch wie zu erwarten, bringt die DSDN-Zerst√∂r-Challenge von Marc Seibold nat√ºrlich auch Schwierigkeiten mit sich. Schlie√ülich hat sich das Jahr 2020 schon so in unsere K√∂pfe, Herzen und Leben eingebrannt, dass sich das nicht mal eben so kaputt machen l√§sst!  Meini wird aber alles geben, um dem Jahr 2020 an seinem letzten Tag zu zeigen, was es uns alles angetan hat! 

SO WAR DAS DSDN-JAHR 2020 

Mit einer fulminanten Zerst√∂r-Challenge verabschieden wir uns vom Jahr 2020! Was haben wir dieses Jahr nicht alles erlebt bei ‚ÄûDas schaffst du nie!‚Äú. Wir starteten mit der 24 Stunden Insel-Challenge und der darauffolgenden, hei√ü ersehnten Achterbahnstrafe f√ºr Marc ins Jahr. Wir f√ºhrten unsere neue Reihe ‚ÄûDSDN Classics‚Äú ein, Ari telefonierte ganz 24 Stunden mit euch, Marc musste endlich alle seine Sozialstrafen ableisten, wir machten drei knallharte Verstecken-Challenges, Meini musste 24 Stunden Autoscooter fahren und und und. Es ging hoch hinaus und wieder tief hinunter, es war eiskalt und wurde richtig hei√ü, es war schmerzhaft, peinlich und unfassbar lustig. Und das alles war wieder mal nur m√∂glich dank eurer gro√üartigen Unterst√ºtzung! Danke liebe DSDN-Community f√ºr euren Support, eure Kommentare und Likes, euer Lob und eure Kritik und die viele Liebe. Wir sehen uns 2021 - wenn hoffentlich alles besser wird. (habe beim Lesen eine kleine Tr√§ne wegdr√ºcken m√ºssen) 

Welches DSDN Video hat euch im Jahr 2020 am‚ÄØbesten‚ÄØund welches am wenigsten gefallen? Schreibt es uns in die Kommentare!‚ÄØ 

 

#DSDN #Dasschaffstdunie #funk #Challenge 

******************************************************************** 

Ob 72 Stunden moderieren, eine Skischanze hochrennen oder eine Skulptur aus Eis schnitzen: Bei ‚ÄûDas schaffst du nie!‚Äú stellt der fiese Redakteur Marc Seibold den zwei Hosts Ariane Alter und Sebastian Meinberg immer abwechselnd eine Challenge ‚Äì gerne auch 24 Stunden lang. Schaffen die Hosts die Challenge, d√ºrfen sie Marc bestrafen. Schaffen sie es nicht, m√ºssen sie noch eine Bestrafung ertragen. Jeden Donnerstag um 15 Uhr gibt‚Äôs ein neues Video von ‚ÄûDas schaffst du nie!‚Äú. Heute: Die Zerst√∂r-Challenge! Auf jede neue Challenge kommt am darauffolgenden Donnerstag die Bestrafung.

snippet.title: Welcome to BREATH - A 30 Day Yoga Journey  |  Yoga With Adriene
snippet.description:
It is happening! Today‚Äôs video is a bit of an orientation, a warm welcome, and an official kick-off. We will begin with a few easy group breaths to enjoy, and recognize that if all you do is arrive here to breathe, you are winning, golden, exactly where you are meant to be. 

You can consider this a practice day for your upcoming practices if you like. 

**IMPORTANT** If you are not signed up for the daily email that corresponds with each practice video, sign up for free and receive your free BREATH calendar here: https://www.yogawithadriene.com/breath

Work with what you have, but in this video, I make some suggestions on some optional things you might like to bring to class each day, along with an invitation to help guide you as you embark on this unique journey. 

Check-in with your willingness to be present, and remember for this to take off - you have to show up.

If this cross-legged position is not doable for you, you can use blankets, blocks, or pillows to sit up on. You can also come into a chair, or on the edge of your couch when we take this shape. That is a great way to modify and possibly a better spot for you to tune in, work with the breath technique, and warm up before we get moving into other shapes each day. 

Finally, set an intention. Be brave and ask WHY? Why are you here? What do you think pulled you here? And if you don‚Äôt know, that is okay, we will likely uncover that together. (How exciting!)

Let me know where you are practicing from in the comment section down below!

snippet.title: Watch Australia's 2021 Sydney Harbour New Year fireworks celebrations
snippet.description:
Watch a 'toned down' firework display in Sydney Harbour this year, as Australia allows New Year's Eve events to happen, but under strict rules and restrictions. 

Anyone who wished to enter the Sydney Harbour 'Green Zone' on New Year's Eve needed to apply for an entry pass, with prime firework vantage points being designated for frontline workers.

People have been encouraged to limit non-essential gatherings over the New Year period where possible to further minimise the risk of transmission in the community.

Subscribe to The Telegraph on YouTube ‚ñ∫ https://bit.ly/3idrdLH

Get the latest headlines: https://www.telegraph.co.uk/

Telegraph.co.uk and YouTube.com/TelegraphTV are websites of The Telegraph, the UK's best-selling quality daily newspaper providing news and analysis on UK and world events, business, sport, lifestyle and culture.

snippet.title: WELCOME TO THE OTHER SIDE [Trailer] ‚Äì join Jean-Michel Jarre on NYE in Virtual Reality NOTRE DAME
snippet.description:
In partnership with @Ville de Paris, and under the patronage of @UNESCO, Electronic Music pioneer @jeanmicheljarre teams up with French VR start-up VRrOOm to take us into the New Year with a live-stream trailblazing concert-spectacular set in the virtual environment of the planetary landmark, Notre-Dame de Paris.

Join & share the party on December 31st, 2020 at 23:25 (CET) & Paris-time: https://youtu.be/VKjFjFtKBRI

Go to www.jeanmicheljarre.com to see how you can watch on Facebook, Twitter, VR, TV and Radio. 

Here is how to join the VR experience: 
Concert:
- Download the VRChat app on Steam, Oculus or Viveport to watch the concert in virtual reality on all PC VR headsets, Oculus Quest and Quest 2 + link cable, or simply via PC
Once in VRChat, check the 'NOTRE-DAME CONCERT' icon in the WORLDS menu to access the concert. Attention, the world will be activated on December 31 at 11:23pm CET only (December 31 at 2:23pm PST).
Quest and Quest 2 users who are not equipped with the link cable will be able to access a lighter version of the concert!

After-party:
- Download the VRChat app on Steam, Oculus or Viveport to watch the concert in virtual reality on all PC VR headsets, Oculus Quest and Quest 2 with or without link cable, or simply via PC
Once in VRChat, check the 'NOTRE-DAME AFTER-PARTY' icon in the WORLDS menu to access the party. Attention, the world will be activated starting January 1 at 00:13pm CET only (December 31 at 3:13pm PST).
Many suprises await you in the after-party world!
 
For all ongoing information follow JMJ on Facebook, Twitter, Instagram and YouTube or check: www.jeanmicheljarre.com
 
Follow Jean-Michel Jarre:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jeanmicheljarre/ 
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/jeanmicheljarre 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jeanmicheljarre/
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/user/jeanmicheljarre?sub_confirmation=1

Choose your music service to listen to Jean Michel Jarre: https://jean-michel-jarre.lnk.to/JMJ 

#VR #NYE #NotreDame

snippet.title: PTBS: So krass ver√§ndert ein Trauma Franzys Leben | reporter
snippet.description:
üò± Trauma, Flashback, Trigger ‚Äì eine Posttraumatische Belastungsst√∂rung (PTBS) haben nicht nur Soldat*innen! PTBS ist eine normale psychische Erkrankung, die viele Ursachen haben kann: Krieg, Folter, Unf√§lle, aber auch sexualisierte Gewalt und andere Gewalterfahrungen. Folgen und Symptome sind vielf√§ltig: Schlafst√∂rungen, Reizbarkeit, Konzentrationsschw√§che. Aber auch das Risikio f√ºr eine Depression steigt. 
Franzy aus Augsburg ist 19 Jahre alt und will √ºber den Ursprung ihrer PTBS nicht sprechen. Fest steht: Sie hat im Alltag durch die Erkrankung heftige Probleme. Aber auch eine gro√üe Hilfe: ihre Assistenzh√ºndin Frieda. üê∂
 
üé∂ Musik: 
Mr Roth, Noah Bentfield, R. Time - Drama Parlour
Mr Roth, Noah Bentfield, R. Time - Trapped in Reality
Cosimo Erario - An Unusual Tomorrow
Moritz Bintig - Strange Things Happen
Florian Thaller - Digital Era
 
üíä Die Assistenzh√ºndin Frieda kann ‚Äúanzeigen‚Äù, wenn sie merkt, dass Franzy einen Anfall bekommt. Wenn es schon zu sp√§t ist, kann Frieda bellen, Medikamente und Hilfe holen. Franzy hat Frieda teilweise selbst ausgebildet, teilweise mithilfe eines professionellen Assistenzhundetrainers. 
 
üêï Assistenzhunde d√ºrfen in der Regel auch Orte betreten, wo Hunde sonst verboten sind, z.B. Superm√§rkte, Krankenh√§user oder Beh√∂rden. Grundlage hierf√ºr sind die UN-Behindertenrechtskonvention (UN-BRK) und das Bundes-Behindertengleichstellungsgesetz (BGG).
Mehr Infos dazu gibt es hier: 
https://www.pfotenpiloten.org/gesetze/#zutritt 
 
üë©‚Äç‚öïÔ∏è Fatima hat vor dem Dreh mit der PTBS-Expertin Ulrike Schultheis gesprochen. Sie ist Chef√§rztin der Abteilung f√ºr Psychosomatische Medizin und Psychotraumatologie der LVR-Klinik K√∂ln ‚Äì dort gibt es auch eine Traumaambulanz. 
 
üòî Frau Schulthei√ü geht davon aus, dass 2-5 Prozent der Gesellschaft eine PTBS haben. Es wird eine Dunkelziffer vermutet, daher gibt es keine genauen Zahlen. Man unterscheidet zwischen einer klassischen (ausgel√∂st durch ein bestimmtes Traumaereignis) und einer komplexen PTBS (augel√∂st durch Gewalt oder andere Traumaerlebnisse √ºber einen l√§ngeren Zeitraum).
 
üìä Die Wahrscheinlichkeit eine PTBS zu bekommen ist Expert*innen zufolge bei Frauen h√∂her als bei M√§nnern ‚Äì weil bei Frauen die Wahrscheinlichkeit h√∂her sei, Gewalt zu erfahren. Sch√§tzungen zufolge liegt die Wahrscheinlichkeit bei Frauen bei 10-12 Prozent und bei M√§nnern bei 5-6 Prozent. Mehr dazu gibt es hier:
https://psychiatrie.charite.de/fuer_patienten/krankheitsbilder/posttraumatische_belastungsstoerungen_ptbs/
Und hier:
https://www.bundestag.de/resource/blob/490504/8acad12ffbf45476eecdfeff7d6bd3f4/wd-9-069-16-pdf-data.pdf 

üÜò Wo gibt‚Äôs Hilfe?
PTBS kann behandelt werden! Mit Psychotherapie und in einigen F√§llen zus√§tzlich mit Medikamenten. Man kann zuerst zur Haus√§rztin gehen, oder direkt zu einem Therapeuten, in eine psychiatrische Klinik oder in eine Traumaambulanz. 
 
üìû Telefonseelsorge:
https://www.telefonseelsorge.de/
Tel: 08001110111 (kostenfrei)
 
üëâ √úbersicht der Traumaambulanzen in Deutschland:
https://www.bmjv.de/SharedDocs/Downloads/DE/Themen/OpferhilfeUndGewaltpr%C3%A4vention/Opferbeauftragter/Uebersicht_Traumaambulanzen.html 
 
 
üéû Team: Fatima Talalini, Gregor Simbruner, Fr√©d√©ric Sapart, Lea Brockmann, Andreas Josef, Julia von Cube
 
üëâ Ihr findet uns auch hier:  
Twitter: https://twitter.com/reporter 
Facebook: http://facebook.com/reporter.offiziell/ 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/reporter.offiziell/ 
Snapchat: https://www.snapchat.com/discover/Reporter/3246991136 
 
üëâ #reporter geh√∂rt zu #funk: 
YouTube: http://youtube.com/funkofficial 
funk Web-App: http://go.funk.net 
Facebook: http://facebook.com/funk
 
Erlebt mit uns echte Storys. Nah dran. Kritisch. Ohne Filter. üíô
Jede Woche ein neues Thema. üé•
 
üññ Hallo! Ich hei√üe Fatima. Ich habe schnell gemerkt: Ich lerne viel mehr √ºber die Welt, wenn ich mit Menschen spreche, die ganz anders sind als ich! Ich will wissen, wie die Welt funktioniert und auf Ideen schauen, wie wir sie besser machen k√∂nnen. Na dann los, K√§ffchen? Instagram: @fatimautopie
 
üëâ reporter wird vom Programmbereich Aktuelles des WDR f√ºr funk produziert. funk ist ein Gemeinschaftsangebot der Arbeitsgemeinschaft der Rundfunkanstalten der Bundesrepublik Deutschland (ARD) und des Zweiten Deutschen Fernsehens (ZDF). http://go.funk.net/impressum

snippet.title: Selbstversuch: Wie geil sind Outdoorabenteuer im Winter? || PULS Reportage
snippet.description:
Urlaub und Abenteuer waren 2020 nicht wirklich drin. Tag ein Tag aus haben wir unsere vier W√§nde betrachtet ‚Äì der Wunsch nach einem Abenteuer ist gro√ü. Und das ist eigentlich ganz leicht m√∂glich, denn ein Mikroabenteuer kann eine gute Abwechslung zum Alltag sein. Unser Reporter Sebastian Meinberg will f√ºr die heutige Reportage eine Nacht unter freiem Sternenhimmel im Winter √ºbernachten. Das macht er selbstverst√§ndlich nicht allein, sondern mit der Outdoor Expertin Anna Hadzelek vom Podcast ‚ÄûBergfreundinnen‚Äú. Wie die Nacht unter freiem Himmel wird und ob Sebastian sich warm genug einpackt, seht ihr in der neuen PULS Reportage.  

√úBERNACHTEN IM FREIEN 

F√ºr dieses Mikroabenteuer haben sich Anna und Sebastian mit einem Schlaf- und Biwaksack auf eine einsame Wiese eines Bekannten gelegt. Denn die rechtliche Lage f√ºr √úbernachtungen im Freien ist  kompliziert und variiert von Bundesland zu Bundesland.  

Aber nicht nur der Ort, sondern auch das Gep√§ck m√ºssen f√ºr ein Mikroabenteuer im Winter gut √ºberlegt sein. Denn trotz aller Abenteuerlust darf man nicht vergessen, dass das √úbernachten bei Minusgraden nicht ungef√§hrlich ist. 

Wo man in der freien Natur √ºbernachten darf und was man hierf√ºr alles im Winter einpacken sollte, k√∂nnt ihr in der PULS Reportage diese Woche erfahren! 

WAS IST EIN MIKROABENTEUER? 

Mikroabenteuer sind kleine Erlebnisse, die sich einfach in den Alltag integrieren lassen. Ziel ist es, dem Alltagsstress zu entfliehen, ohne viel Geld ausgeben oder weit reisen zu m√ºssen. Mikroabenteuer k√∂nnen ganz kleine Aktionen sein: mit einer unbekannten Buslinie einfach mal bis zur Endhaltestelle fahren und sich dort umsehen. Oder in der eigenen Stadt immer abwechselnd links und rechts abzubiegen, um neue Viertel zu entdecken. Mikroabenteuer k√∂nnen aber auch Wochenendtrips sein, bei denen man bis zum n√§chsten See l√§uft und dort √ºbernachtet oder wie in dieser Reportage eine √úbernachtung unter freiem Sternenhimmel im Winter. 

Mehr von Anna und ihren Freundinnen k√∂nnt ihr im Podcast ‚ÄûBergfreundinnen‚Äú h√∂ren: 

https://www.br.de/mediathek/podcast/bergfreundinnen/834 

Redaktion: Maria Christoph, Heike Schuffenhauer, Hendrick Rack 
Kamera: Jonas Julian K√∂ck, Denis L√ºthi, Felix Holderer 
Schnitt: Marion V√∂lker 
Grafik: Daniel Gro√ühans 
Channel Management: Christian Tim To 
----------------------------------------------------------- 
PULS REPORTAGE AUF INSTAGRAM 

Memes, mitmachen, noch mehr Infos: Auf Instagram nimmt euch Nadine mit hinter die Kulissen von PULS Reportage ‚Äì und Ari und Meini sind nat√ºrlich auch am Start! 

‚ñ∫ Folgt uns auf Instagram: 
http://www.instagram.com/pulsreportage/  

DIE PULS REPORTAGE PLAYLIST 

In unserer Playlist gibt's die Songs aus den Videos. Jede Woche neu! 

‚ñ∫ Spotify 
http://open.spotify.com/playlist/74OFxHZno6e9MI66WkGugj 

‚ñ∫ Apple Music 
https://music.apple.com/de/playlist/die-ari-meini-playlist/pl.bc5d28fc996d434c85aef6c6004d0211  

----------------------------------------------------------- 
Hi! Wir sind Ariane Alter, Nadine Hadad und Sebastian Meinberg von PULS Reportage! In unseren Videos gehen wir jede Woche spannenden Fragen nach und starten gerne mal Selbstversuche. 

Jeden Mittwoch um 15 Uhr gibt‚Äôs eine neue PULS Reportage! 

‚ñ∫ Folgt Nadine auf Instagram: 
https://www.instagram.com/nadine_hadad/  

‚ñ∫ Erlebt Sebastians Selbstexperimente live: 
https://instagram.com/heinz.wescher/  

Schreib uns in die Kommentare, was dich bewegt ‚Äì wir wagen den Selbsttest und probieren es f√ºr dich aus!
